snippet.title: Marvel's THE BLACK CAT Teaser Trailer - Netflix Concept | Amber Heard, Vincent D'Onofrio
snippet.description:
Non-profit, fan-made trailer. No copyright infringement intended.

With the rise in popularity of Miss Felicia Hardy since her appearance in #SpiderMan PS4, I thought it only fair to make a second #BlackCat trailer! 


________________________________

Thumbnail is an edit of an awesome cosplay by DanielleDeNicola, check her out:
http://danielledenicola.com/#home
https://www.instagram.com/danielledenicola/?hl=en

If you haven't seen the first Black Cat fan trailer, check it out here:
https://www.youtube.com/edit?o=U&video_id=zFHpzAoz5SU


Subscribe for more and enjoy!



________________________________

Copyright Disclaimer: This video is protected under fair use. It uses brief clippings of existing media to communicate a new concept/idea that fans are able to consume as either celebratory or theoretical commentary on how a film/cinematic universe could look. This is often intended as parody and/or feminist critique on the typical male hero-trope either by providing light on female heroism in its place or by mimicking action trailer themes. It draws upon existing art to suggest new ventures and/or propose changes to current products.

#BlackCat #SpiderMan #MCU
